来不多过问。每年家庭生活和还贷开销很大，基本都是我在撑。 我自己是金融行业中层，而且还是偏业务向的，虽然赚的还可以，但懂得都知道这工作有多累，哪怕就这样回家还得管孩子学习，等孩子睡了，我老婆还给我安排了考 CFA 的任务，还得看书。讲真的，我就没怎么在自己身上花钱，娱乐也就是偶尔去看个电影。 我本以为我做到这样，买台 PS 已经可以得到老婆的理解，结果还是被说不务正业，所以一时间委屈也好、生气也好，就爆发出来了。 想当初没有结婚前我也曾是追风少年，现在却生生活成了一个社畜、一个供养者、一台赚钱机器。这难道就是中年男人的宿命？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-9642e8414b3fe422511025575385ff2f_1440w.webp"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/589008739"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I3J6p+absoag1EAMaCDkzMTcyNjA0IJS0sqAGMBM4+gNAF3IJNTg5MDA4NzM5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "24_1679760553.7107096", "card_id": "Q_591500081", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 162}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "编造黄谣会给女性受害人造成什么伤害？女性因此而感到伤害的根源是什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-46827a6a1ebbb822104c252c40337b92_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/591500081"}}, "attached_info": "ClUI3J6p+absoag1EAMaCDkzNzI2MTg5IJ2y8aAGMA040AFAGHIJNTkxNTAwMDgxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "25_1679760553.7114835", "card_id": "Q_476353592", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 47}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "有哪些较冷门但意义重大的考古发现？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-79e2bff5d2359675d1ecea19710ef3ef_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://ww